abstract: The following letter from EDWAED SPANGLER, now a prisoner at the Dry Tortugas, was recently received in Baltimore: FORT JEFFERSON, Fla., Sept. 6, 1867. abstract: The newspaper controversy between Major JAS. D. WALKER and Col. J.
